  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Dependencies & Cascading Failures\n\nMicroservices share fate through **shared dependencies**. One Redis outage can break cart-service \u2192 order-service \u2192 payment flow.\n\n**Blast radius:** Map which services fail when a dependency fails.\n\n| Dependency | If down | Affected services |\n|------------|---------|-------------------|\n| Redis | Cart can't store items | cart-service, order-service (checkout) |\n| RabbitMQ | Events not delivered | order-service, notification-service |\n| CNPG Postgres | Data unavailable | product, user, order, payment |\n| product-service | Catalog/stock unknown | cart, order, api-gateway |\n\n**Exercise:** Simulate Redis failure (`kubectl scale deploy redis -n ecommerce --replicas=0`). Watch error rate propagate upstream on RED dashboard.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Redis ready",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "value"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "kube_pod_status_ready{namespace=\"ecommerce\",pod=~\"redis-.*\",condition=\"true\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Redis ready",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
